high_descs: Move forward and turn right to face the table with the TV on it.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Turn left, go toward the couch, then turn left, step forward, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Put the credit card in the box on the table.
Pick up the box from the table.
Turn around to face the couch.
Put the box on the left couch cushion.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a credit card in it on the couch.

high_descs: Take five steps forward then turn right to face the TV on a table.
Pick up the credit card from the table; in front of the TV.
Turn left for two steps, take another left and walk four steps, then turn left and stop in front of the coffee table.
Place the credit card on the left side of  the cardboard box, sitting in the middle of the coffee table.
Pick up the cardboard box.
Turn right for one step, turn right again and stop in front of the red couch.
Put the cardboard box at the far right of the left side cushion on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box, with a credit card inside, on the couch.

high_descs: Go to the TV table
Pick up a credit card from the table
Go to the center table
Put the credit card in a box
Pick up the box
Go to the red sofa
Put the box down on the red sofa
anns.task_desc: Put a credit card in a box and move it to a sofa
